### Conversation Participant - Add (manual IDs)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/conversation-participants/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "conversation": {{conversationId}},
  "user": {{userId}}
}

### Message - Send (manual)
# @name createMessage
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/messages/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "conversation": {{conversationId}},
  "sender": {{userId}},
  "message_type": "text",
  "text": "Hi, I need the front bumper for Corolla 2018.",
  "client_timestamp": "2026-03-20T12:00:00Z"
}

### Message Status - Add
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/message-statuses/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "message": {{messageId}},
  "user": {{userId}},
  "status": "sent"
}

